Name: Assets
Condition: not Assets and LiabilitiesAndEquity CurrentAssets == LiabilitiesAndEquity

Name: Assets
Condition: not Assets and not NoncurrentAssets and LiabilitiesAndEquity and LiabilitiesAndEquity == (Liabilities + Equity)

Name: NoncurrentAssets
Condition: Assets and CurrentAssets

Name: LiabilitiesAndEquity
Condition: not LiabilitiesAndEquity and Assets

Name: Equity
Condition: EquityAttributableToNoncontrollingInterest and EquityAttributableToParent

Name: Equity
Condition: not Equity and not EquityAttributableToNoncontrollingInterest and EquityAttributableToParent

Name: Equity
Condition: not Equity

Name: EquityAttributableToParent
Condition: Equity and EquityAttributableToNoncontrollingInterest and not EquityAttributableToParent
Description: Impute Equity attributable to parent based on existence of equity and noncontrolling interest.

Name: EquityAttributableToParent
Condition: Equity and not EquityAttributableToNoncontrollingInterest and not EquityAttributableToParent
Description: Impute Equity attributable to parent based on existence of equity and noncontrolling interest.

Name: Liabilities
Condition: not Liabilities and Equity

Name: NoncurrentLiabilities
Condition: Liabilities and CurrentLiabilities
Description: This seems incorrect because liabilities might not be reported

Name: Liabilities
Condition: not Liabilities and CurrentLiabilities and not NoncurrentLiabilities

Name: lngBSCheck3
Condition: CurrentAssets or NoncurrentAssets or CurrentLiabilities or NoncurrentLiabilities
Description: if current assets/liabilities are zero and noncurrent assets/liabilities;: don't do this test because the balance sheet is not classified

Name: lngBSCheck4
Condition: CurrentAssets or NoncurrentAssets or CurrentLiabilities or NoncurrentLiabilities
Description: if current assets/liabilities are zero and noncurrent assets/liabilities;: don't do this test because the balance sheet is not classified

Name: NetIncomeAvailableToCommonStockholdersBasic
Condition: not NetIncomeAvailableToCommonStockholdersBasic and not PreferredStockDividendsAndOtherAdjustments and NetIncomeAttributableToParent

Name: IncomeFromContinuingOperationsAfterTax
Condition: NetIncomeLoss and not IncomeFromContinuingOperationsAfterTax

Name: NetIncomeAttributableToParent
Condition: not NetIncomeAttributableToParent and not NetIncomeAttributableToNoncontrollingInterest and NetIncomeLoss

Name: PreferredStockDividendsAndOtherAdjustments
Condition: not PreferredStockDividendsAndOtherAdjustments and NetIncomeAttributableToParent and NetIncomeAvailableToCommonStockholdersBasic

Name: ComprehensiveIncome
Condition: not ComprehensiveIncomeAttributableToParent and not ComprehensiveIncomeAttributableToNoncontrollingInterest and not ComprehensiveIncome and not OtherComprehensiveIncome

Name: OtherComprehensiveIncome
Condition: ComprehensiveIncome and not OtherComprehensiveIncome

Name: ComprehensiveIncomeAttributableToParent
Condition: not ComprehensiveIncomeAttributableToParent and not ComprehensiveIncomeAttributableToNoncontrollingInterest and ComprehensiveIncome

Name: IncomeFromContinuingOperationsBeforeTax
Condition: IncomeBeforeEquityMethodInvestments and IncomeFromEquityMethodInvestments and not IncomeFromContinuingOperationsBeforeTax

Name: IncomeFromContinuingOperationsBeforeTax
Condition: not IncomeFromContinuingOperationsBeforeTax and IncomeFromContinuingOperationsAfterTax

Name: IncomeFromContinuingOperationsAfterTax
Condition: not IncomeFromContinuingOperationsAfterTax and (IncomeTaxExpenseBenefit or not IncomeTaxExpenseBenefit) and IncomeFromContinuingOperationsBeforeTax

Name: GrossProfit
Condition: not GrossProfit and Revenues and CostOfRevenue

Name: GrossProfit
Condition: not GrossProfit and Revenues and CostOfRevenue

Name: Revenues
Condition: not GrossProfit and not Revenues and CostOfRevenue

Name: CostOfRevenue
Condition: GrossProfit and Revenues and not CostOfRevenue

Name: CostsAndExpenses
Condition: not GrossProfit and not CostsAndExpenses and CostOfRevenue and OperatingExpenses

Name: CostsAndExpenses
Condition: not CostsAndExpenses and OperatingExpenses and CostOfRevenue

Name: CostsAndExpenses
Condition: not GrossProfit and not CostsAndExpenses and Revenues and OperatingIncomeLoss and OtherOperatingIncome

Name: OperatingExpenses
Condition: CostOfRevenue and CostsAndExpenses and not OperatingExpenses

Name: CostOfRevenue
Condition: Revenues and not GrossProfit and (Revenues - CostsAndExpenses == OperatingIncomeLoss) and not OperatingExpenses and not OtherOperatingIncome

Name: IncomeBeforeEquityMethodInvestments
Condition: not IncomeBeforeEquityMethodInvestments and IncomeFromContinuingOperationsBeforeTax

Name: InterestAndDebtExpense
Condition: OperatingIncomeLoss and NonoperatingIncomeLoss and not InterestAndDebtExpense and IncomeBeforeEquityMethodInvestments

Name: OtherOperatingIncome
Condition: GrossProfit and OperatingExpenses and OperatingIncomeLoss

Name: IncomeBeforeEquityMethodInvestments
Condition: IncomeFromEquityMethodInvestments and IncomeBeforeEquityMethodInvestments and IncomeBeforeEquityMethodInvestments != IncomeFromContinuingOperationsBeforeTax

Name: OperatingIncomeLoss
Condition: IncomeFromEquityMethodInvestments and IncomeBeforeEquityMethodInvestments and IncomeBeforeEquityMethodInvestments != IncomeFromContinuingOperationsBeforeTax

Name: OperatingIncomeLoss
Condition: not OperatingIncomeLoss and IncomeBeforeEquityMethodInvestments
Description: DANGEROUS!! May need to turn off. IS3 had 2085 PASSES WITHOUT this imputing. if it is higher,: keep the test

Name: NonoperatingIncomeLossPlusInterestAndDebtExpense
Condition: not NonoperatingIncomeLossPlusInterestAndDebtExpense and NonoperatingIncomePlusInterestAndDebtExpensePlusIncomeFromEquityMethodInvestments

Name: NetCashFlowsDiscontinued
Condition: not NetCashFlowsDiscontinued

Name: NetCashFlowsOperatingContinuing
Condition: NetCashFlowsOperating and not NetCashFlowsOperatingContinuing

Name: NetCashFlowsInvestingContinuing
Condition: NetCashFlowsInvesting and not NetCashFlowsInvestingContinuing

Name: NetCashFlowsFinancingContinuing
Condition: NetCashFlowsFinancing and not NetCashFlowsFinancingContinuing

Name: NetCashFlowsOperating
Condition: NetCashFlowsOperating==0 and NetCashFlowsOperatingContinuing and NetCashFlowsOperatingDiscontinued==0

Name: NetCashFlowsInvesting
Condition: NetCashFlowsInvesting==0 and NetCashFlowsInvestingContinuing and NetCashFlowsInvestingDiscontinued==0

Name: NetCashFlowsFinancing
Condition: NetCashFlowsFinancing==0 and NetCashFlowsFinancingContinuing and NetCashFlowsFinancingDiscontinued==0

Name: NetCashFlow
Condition: NetCashFlow==0 and (NetCashFlowsOperating or NetCashFlowsInvesting or NetCashFlowsFinancing)

Name: SGR
Preference: eval(((NetIncomeLoss / Revenues) * (1 + ((Assets - Equity) / Equity))) / ((1 / (Revenues / Assets)) - (((NetIncomeLoss / Revenues) * (1 + (((Assets - Equity) / Equity)))))))
